## 🧠 Architecture Notes

- Follows MVC pattern
- Separation of concerns (Routes → Controller → Model)
- Designed for microservice migration in future
- Schema optimized for indexing and search

---

## 📦 Future Improvements

- Redis caching for product listing
- Pagination & cursor-based pagination
- Cloudinary image upload integration
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Event-driven architecture (Kafka/RabbitMQ)

